name: 小鸟，去除速度检测，红绿灯检测，头盔，零售单过滤
description: 小鸟去检测和零售单
rules:
  - domain: aiot.ele.me, REJECT # 这种不影响流程的可以直接拒绝

map_locals:
  - match: ^https?://.*amap\.com/ws/mps/rtt
    status_code: 200
    body: '{}'
  - match: ^https?://.*ele\.me/.*(retail|supermarket)
    status_code: 200
    body: '{}'
  - match: ^https?://.*ele\.me/.*(helmet|detect|speed)
    status_code: 200
    body: '{}'
mitm:
  hostnames:
    - "*.amap.com"
    - "*.ele.me"
